#DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Former Deputy Finance Minister Mcebisi Jonas is calling for changes to the political system. He says this is the only way to fight corruption. READ: Corruption is a threat to democracy, says Rev Chikane Jonas says the electoral system must be made more inclusive. "The crisis is the political system. As long as we look at individuals and think that we have messiahs who can solve the problem, then we are still going to be stuck where we are," he said. Watch the video above for more details.